• Graduates swear to false affidavit to meet up age requirements 
• Parents seek govt’s intervention With the high level of unemployment and underemployment, prolonged strikes by the Academic Staff Union of Universities (ASUU) and its polytechnic counterpart, Academic Staff Union of Polytechnics (ASUP), have raised concerns about the country’s rising dependency ratio, as majority of youths are becoming idle by the day.  According to him, employers are faced with the challenge of retraining people who are fully formed or left school for long before being engaged. 